{"tid":1317159,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］行使公民權力制服懷疑冒警嘅人是否可行","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:35.000Z","uid":49028,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02e5674374e43061b25dac74ba8ad052e451b664","tid":1317159,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:38:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">相信大家都有注意時事新聞<br />\n法國有好多冇警員編號及委任證嘅人<br />\n配備不同程度嘅攻擊性武器<br />\n並向普通市民進行揮舞 詷嚇動作<br />\n意圖制造混亂 他人的生命及財產安全 <br />\n破壞警民合作關係</span><br />\n<br />\n而一般他們干犯了<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 冒警<br />\n2. 藏有攻擊性武器<br />\n3.公眾地方行為不檢<br />\n4.蓄意傷人<br />\n5.企圖謀殺<br />\n6.非法持有槍枝 </span></span>等等<br />\n<br />\n為改善情況<br />\n可以進一步組織糾察小隊<br />\n並每隊配備<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.大聲公（於拘捕前進行警告及表示拘捕理由）<br />\n2.banner (同上. 避免罪犯及傳媒選擇性失明或失聰）<br />\n3.索帶（控制罪犯）<br />\n4.基本防護裝備（保護民間糾察隊員）<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下開放討論方案可行性和改善方案</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">頭盔聲明：純學術討論<br />\n於此post任何非法討論或行為<br />\n均與本人無關</span></span>"},{"pid":"be0571dbfc6357bcd1d7ac54f8ae21b11f866f7b","tid":1317159,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:40:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3325d79a52a9f78c47c92f52e9b21b1090c90c91","tid":1317159,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75aed9c5b291f395598f358562d65953503cdf7","tid":1317159,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c17d8cba561ad3c7b288d157d886ccfc36c773","tid":1317159,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,